ed\npreviously. Criteria to identify provenance of Lapis Lazuli from four of the\nmain sources (Afghanistan, Pamir Mountains in Tajikistan, Chile and Siberia)\nwere proposed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Aug 2016 09:50:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-29"}
