-chronometer is confirmed to be the most resilient to\ntheoretical production ratios and yields an age of 16.5+:-6.6 Gyr. Lead (Pb) is\nalso tentatively detected in CS 29497-004, at a level compatible with a scaled\nSolar r-process, or with the theoretical expectations for a pure r-process in\nthis star.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 Aug 2016 13:57:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-22"}
